BETTER_AUTH_SECRET=your-better-auth-secret-minimum-32-characters-CHANGE-THIS

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Notes:
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the browser
# 2. Never put sensitive keys (API keys, secrets) in NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables
